<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lan="en">

    <head>
        <% include ../partials/head %>
        <link href="/css/carousel.css" rel="stylesheet">
    </head>

    <body>
        <% include ../partials/header %>


        <!-- Carousel
        ================================================== -->
        <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <!-- Indicators -->
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                <div class="item active">
                    <img class="first-slide" src="/img/chessBoard.jpg" alt="First slide">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="carousel-caption">
                            <div class="home-container">
                                <a href="quickcreate">
                                    <img class="home-img" src="img/bracketSample.jpg" alt="brackets">
                                    <h4>Try Our Bracket Generator</h4>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                            <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="/signup" role="button">Sign up today</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img class="second-slide"  src="/img/swimming.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="carousel-caption">
                            <div class="home-container">
                                <a href="leaderboard">
                                    <img class="home-img" src="img/podium.png" alt="Podium">
                                    <h4>View Leaderboards</h4>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                            <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="/signup" role="button">Sign up today</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img class="third-slide" src="/img/running.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="carousel-caption">
                            <div class="home-container">
                                <a href="signup">
                                    <img class="home-img" src="img/joinUs.jpg" alt="brackets">
                                    <h4>Sign up for FREE!</h4>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                            <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="/signup" role="button">Sign up today</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
        </div><!-- /.carousel -->


        <!-- Marketing messaging and featurettes
        ================================================== -->
        <!-- Wrap the rest of the page in another container to center all the content. -->

        <div class="container marketing">

            <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <img class="img-circle" src="/img/question_mark.png" alt="question_mark" width="140" height="140">
                    <h3>What we do</h3>
                    <p class="index-content-p">
                        Our site allows users to join organizations that they are a part of. Further to this, they will
                        be able to join leagues and tournaments that they also participate in. The leagues will have
                        a ranking system in which users can compete to get to the top. We will provide organizations
                        with tools to track their matches, create tournaments and provide a community for their members
                        to communicate.
                    </p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/about" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
                </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <img class="img-circle" src="/img/magnifying_glass.png" alt="magnifying_glass" width="140" height="140">
                    <h3>Who We are</h3>
                    <p class="index-content-p">
                        We are a small company consisting of four elite team members. Our team is passionate about
                        recreational sports and computer science. Each member has their own favorite sport which makes
                        this website unique as it will provide a wide range of expertise. We are looking forward to
                        creating and growing a friendly community that will make everyone feel comfortable.
                    </p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/about" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
                </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <img class="img-circle" src="/img/globe.png" alt="question_mark" width="140" height="140">
                    <h3>What This site Does</h3>
                    <p class="index-content-p">
                        The main goal of this website will be to help organizations and clubs manage their own internal
                        rankings and leaderboards. It will allow for organizations to create their own tournaments
                        and track its member participants. The site is meant to save time and money for those wanting
                        wanting an easy-to-use site with lots of functionality.
                    </p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/about" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
                </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
            </div><!-- /.row -->

        </div>

        <% include ../partials/footer %>
    </body>
</html>